---
title: Garlic Bocconcini Bites with a Balsamic Spinach Salad and DIY Croutons
description: Creamy, fresh bocconcini and golden breadcrumbs are fused with garlic puree to create moreish cheesy bites! To cut through the richness, we've added a crisp salad with DIY croutons and balsamic glaze.
